---
---
<section style="
  min-height: 92vh;
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  padding: 80px 24px;
  background: #ffffff;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
">
  <!-- Subtle background decoration -->
  <div style="
    position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0;
    width: 55%; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8eef2 0%, #d4e4f0 100%);
    clip-path: polygon(12% 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);
  "></div>

  <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; position: relative; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; align-items: center;">

    <!-- Left: Typography -->
    <div>
      <p style="
        font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.3em;
        color: #0d8a87; font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 24px; text-transform: uppercase;
      ">⚓ Hakodate Community Media</p>

      <h1 style="
        font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
        font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 60px);
        font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.3;
        color: #0d0d0d; margin-bottom: 28px;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      ">
        知らなかった、<br>
        <span style="color: #0d2d52;">ハコダテ</span><span style="color: #0d8a87;">がある。</span>
      </h1>

      <p style="
        font-size: 15px; color: #6c757d; line-height: 1.9;
        margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 480px;
      ">
        港町・函館に住む人、訪れる人、移住を考える人へ。<br>
        地元目線で、かってに函館の魅力を発信するコミュニティメディアです。
      </p>

      <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/articles" style="
          padding: 14px 32px;
          background: #0d2d52; color: white;
          font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
          border-radius: 4px; transition: all 0.2s;
          letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        "
        onmouseover="this.style.background='#0d4a72'"
        onmouseout="this.style.background='#0d2d52'"
        >記事を読む</a>

        <a href="/about" style="
          padding: 14px 32px;
          border: 1.5px solid #0d2d52; color: #0d2d52;
          font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
          border-radius: 4px; transition: all 0.2s;
          letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        "
        onmouseover="this.style.background='#0d2d52'; this.style.color='white'"
        onmouseout="this.style.background='transparent'; this.style.color='#0d2d52'"
        >サイトについて</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <div style="
        display: flex; gap: 40px; margin-top: 56px;
        padding-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e6ea;
      ">
        {[
          { num: '14', label: '記事' },
          { num: '6', label: 'カテゴリ' },
          { num: '4', label: '仕掛け人' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div>
            <p style="font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; color: #0d2d52; line-height: 1;">{item.num}</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 4px; letter-spacing: 0.1em;">{item.label}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Visual -->
    <div style="position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
      <!-- カッチンメインビジュアル -->
      <div style="
        background: linear-gradient(160deg, #e8eef2 0%, #d4e4f0 100%);
        border-radius: 16px; padding: 40px;
        position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        width: 100%;
      ">
        <!-- Decorative circles -->
        <div style="position: absolute; top: -40px; right: -40px; width: 200px; height: 200px; background: rgba(13,42,82,0.06); border-radius: 50%;"></div>
        <div style="position: absolute; bottom: -20px; left: -20px; width: 120px; height: 120px; background: rgba(13,138,135,0.08); border-radius: 50%;"></div>

        <img
          src="/images/kacchin-nightview.png"
          alt="カッチン — カッテニハコダテのマスコット"
          style="
            width: 100%; max-width: 380px;
            display: block; margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative; z-index: 1;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 16px 40px rgba(13,45,82,0.18));
          "
        />

        <!-- Caption -->
        <p style="
          text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;
          font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
          font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #0d2d52;
          position: relative; z-index: 1;
          letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        ">カッチン（マスコット）</p>
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 4px; position: relative; z-index: 1;">港町ハコダテを見つめるタコ</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Floating badge -->
      <div style="
        position: absolute; top: -16px; right: -8px;
        background: #c05a3a; color: white;
        padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(192,90,58,0.4);
        text-align: center; line-height: 1.4;
        z-index: 2;
      ">
        <div style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 4px;">🦑</div>
        <div>函館発</div>
        <div>ローカル情報</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
